{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/shops-and-services/theatre-film-and-other-artistic-performances","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Theatre, film and other artistic performances","meta_description":"Theatre, film and other artistic performances including circuses and variety shows can no longer take place for the public.","content":{"processed":"<h2>Rules and recommendations</h2>\n<p><strong>Theatre, film and other artistic performances</strong> including circuses and variety shows <strong>can no longer take place for the public</strong>. Scheduled performances must be moved or cancelled. </p>\n<p>It is <strong>virtually impossible</strong> to operate for cinemas. In fact, the presence of any audience is banned, this applies for both indoors and outdoors shows.</p>\n<p>Rehearsals in theatres without the presence of the public may take place. <strong>Exceptions from the obligation to wear a face mask</strong> apply to artists who are <strong>performing on stage</strong> - ie actors, singers and dancers. Moderators, editors or other persons appearing on the radio or television do not have to wear a face mask. However, it is always necessary to not exceed the <strong>limit of 5 singers </strong>indoors. The reason is that singing is very risky in terms of the spread of the virus as there is a large spread of droplets.</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/theatre-film-and-other-artistic-performances"},"changed":"2020-11-29T22:11:24+00:00","valid_from":null,"langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-05T14:23:25+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://www.businessinfo.cz/clanky/program-covid-kultura-podavani-zadosti-o-podporu-bylo-spusteno/","title":"Details on the COVID-Culture (COVID-Kultura in cz) programme "}],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"movie_creation"},"situation_type":{"name":"Shops and services","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services"},"r